articles.title: About this blog
articles.contents:
I’m Daniel Banki, a PhD student in Economics at Universitat Pompeu Fabra in Barcelona, Spain. I work on topics related to judgment and decision making. I use this blog to share some of the things I work on in my free time.
Contact
Please feel free to reach out to me at @banki_daniel.
